title: Green Party Presidential Town Hall - CNN 2016-08-17 -480p Webrip
description:
A WebRip of the CNN townhall with Green Party presidential candidate Jill Stein and VP candidate Ajamu Baraka.

This is a recording without commercials.

A premiere on US television! Never before has there been a townhall with Green party candidates. Its a joy to watch - so refreshing! Enjoy!

And... vote FOR something in the 2016 election!

Trump is a neo-fascist who will divide the US and plunge the world into a desaster!
Clinton is in bed with the establishment, the banks, corporate power and the war profiteers!

So vote for alternatives! Vote FOR a candidate who tackles one of the most important problems of our time: Climate Change!
